ទំរង់កត់ត្រាការអង្កេតជំងឺគ្រុនចាញ់ / PREVALENCE FORM
Field Label:
នាមខ្លួននិងនាមត្រកូលអ្នកអង្កេតការសិក្សារឺអ្នកសំភាស?
What is the investigator name?

កាលបរិច្ឆេទការអង្កេតការសិក្សារឺការសំភាស?
What is the visit date?
លេខកូដអ្នកជ្រើសរើសចូលរួមក្នុងការសិក្សា? What is the subject identifier? [Refer to available list. Do NOT attribute the same identifier to another household once you've allocated it]

មោះរបស់អ្្នកជ្រើសរើសចូលរួមក្នុងការសិក្សា?
What is the name of the subject?

We are going to ask you questions related to malaria exposure. We are interested in the place you live and the measures you take to protect yourself from being bitten by mosquitoes. We will also ask questions about past and ongoing medical treatments, and take a small blood sample to look for the presence of malaria parasites.

Section Header: ការធ្វើដំណើរចេញក្រៅភូមិ / Trips outside the village
Field Label: Here we are interested by knowing where the subject has been to during his trip(s) away from the village over the last month. For each trip outside of the village, we would like to know about the place where the subject has been and for how long he stayed there. These questions are not related to the place where the subject usually work, as these will be asked later in the questionnaire.

តើអ្នកមានចាកចេញពីភូមិទេកាលពីខែមុនហើយអ្នកមានដេកយប់នៅទីនោះទេ?
Has the subject left the village in the last month and spent at least a night away?
Choices, Calculations, OR Slider Labels: 1, មាន (Yes) | 0, មិនមាន (No)

Field Label: Please enter some details about the places the subject has been to when he left the village. You can enter up to 5 different places in the fields below. Leave the remaining fields blank. More specific questions will be asked later in this form about going away from the village for work reasons.

Section Header: កន្លែងធ្វើការងារ / Work places
Field Label: We are now going to ask you questions about the places where you have been for work in the last two months. For each place where you have visited, we will ask some details about how often you have been there and the protection measures you took to prevent malaria.
តើអ្នកមានទៅនិងធ្វើការនៅទីកន្លែងដូចដែលបានរៀបរាប់ខាងក្រោមនេះទេកាលពី២ខែមុន? Did the subject go and work in any of these places in the last 2 months? [Multiple answers possible]

Choices, Calculations, OR Slider Labels: 1, រៀងរាល់ថ្ងៃ (Daily) | 2, ២ទៅ៣ដងក្នុង១អាទិត្យ (Several times a week) | 3, ១ដងក្នុង១អាទិត្យ (Once a week) | 4, ២ទៅ៣ដង​ក្នុង១ខែ (Several times a month) | 5, ១​ដងក្នុង១ខែ (Once a month) | 6, ១ដង (Once)
